    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You perform an Iaido-like attack, which deals damage as though holding the weapon with both hands, and deals an additional 1d6 bonus damage per 2 levels (up to 4d6). If hit, the target suffers 1d4 temporary Dexterity damage for 5 minutes (Fortitude negates). Each time the target is attacked with this technique again within a 24 hour period grants it a cumulative +2 bonus to the save.</p>\n\n\n\n",
